        'privacy.controller.title': '1. Controller',
        'privacy.accessData.title': '2. Access data / Hosting',
        'privacy.accessData.text1': 'When this website is accessed, information is automatically sent by the browser used on your device to the website server. This information is temporarily stored in so-called log files. The collected data may include:',
        'privacy.accessData.item1': 'IP address',
        'privacy.accessData.item2': 'Date and time of access',
        'privacy.accessData.item3': 'Visited pages/URLs',
        'privacy.accessData.item4': 'Referrer URL (previously visited page)',
        'privacy.accessData.item5': 'Browser type and version',
        'privacy.accessData.item6': 'Operating system',
        'privacy.accessData.text2': 'Processing is carried out on the basis of Art. 6 (1) lit. f GDPR. The legitimate interest follows from the purpose of ensuring the stability and security of the website.',
        'privacy.vercel.title': '3. Hosting via Vercel',
        'privacy.vercel.text1': 'This website is hosted by Vercel Inc., 340 S Lemon Ave #4133, Walnut, CA 91789, USA (“Vercel”). When visiting the website, your data is processed on Vercel servers.',
        'privacy.vercel.text2': 'Vercel may store log files and technical data to ensure the security and functionality of the platform. Processing may also take place in the USA.',
        'privacy.vercel.text3': 'The legal basis is Art. 6 (1) lit. f GDPR (legitimate interest in secure and performant hosting).',
        'privacy.vercel.text4': 'More information can be found in Vercel’s privacy policy:',
        'privacy.youtube.title': '4. Embedded YouTube videos',
        'privacy.youtube.text1': 'Videos from YouTube (Google Ireland Limited, Gordon House, Barrow Street, Dublin 4, Ireland) may be embedded on this website.',
        'privacy.youtube.text2': 'When accessing a page with an embedded YouTube video, a connection to YouTube servers is established. Your IP address is transmitted and cookies or similar technologies may be used.',
        'privacy.youtube.text3': 'Depending on the implementation, the legal basis is:',
        'privacy.youtube.item1': 'Art. 6 (1) lit. a GDPR (consent), if you have agreed to this through a cookie/consent banner;',
        'privacy.youtube.item2': 'or Art. 6 (1) lit. f GDPR (legitimate interest), for example in an attractive presentation of the website.',
        'privacy.youtube.text4': 'More information about data processing by YouTube/Google can be found at:',
        'privacy.cookies.title': '5. Cookies',
        'privacy.cookies.text1': 'This website may use cookies or similar technologies, especially when embedded services such as YouTube are used. Cookies are small text files stored on your device.',
        'privacy.cookies.text2': 'You can configure your browser so that no cookies are stored or so that a notice appears before a cookie is stored. If cookies are completely disabled, the functionality of the website may be limited.',
        'privacy.contact.title': '6. Contact',
        'privacy.contact.text1': 'If you contact me by email, the data you provide (e.g. name, email address, message content) will be processed to handle your request.',
        'privacy.contact.text2': 'The legal basis is Art. 6 (1) lit. b GDPR (contract initiation or performance) or Art. 6 (1) lit. f GDPR (legitimate interest in responding to inquiries).',
        'privacy.storage.title': '7. Storage duration',
        'privacy.storage.text': 'Personal data is stored only as long as necessary for the stated purposes or as long as statutory retention periods apply.',
        'privacy.rights.title': '8. Your rights',
        'privacy.rights.text1': 'Under the GDPR, you have the following rights in particular:',
        'privacy.rights.item1': 'Right of access (Art. 15 GDPR)',
        'privacy.rights.item2': 'Right to rectification (Art. 16 GDPR)',
        'privacy.rights.item3': 'Right to erasure (Art. 17 GDPR)',
        'privacy.rights.item4': 'Right to restriction of processing (Art. 18 GDPR)',
        'privacy.rights.item5': 'Right to data portability (Art. 20 GDPR)',
        'privacy.rights.item6': 'Right to object (Art. 21 GDPR)',
        'privacy.rights.text2': 'You also have the right to lodge a complaint with a competent supervisory authority if you believe that the processing of your personal data violates data protection regulations.',
        'privacy.update.title': '9. Updates to this privacy policy',
        'privacy.update.text': 'This privacy policy may be updated when necessary, for example if the website or legal requirements change. The current version applies.',
